               <h1 class="block-title post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">
                Hungarian Paper Money by Barbara Bernt
               </h1>
               <div class="single-top-social-wrap single-social-wrap">
                <span class="single-social-title">
                 share on:
                </span>
                <a class="share-to-social color-facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http://www.faithistorment.com/2015/02/hungarian-paper-money-by-barbara-bernat.html" onclick="window.open(this.href, 'mywin', 'left=50,top=50,width=600,height=350,toolbar=0'); return false;">

              <div class="post-body entry-content post-excerpt" id="post-body-256033753018850014" itemprop="articleBody">
               <div class="mtl-post-content">
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-j9dZga8GI2s/VNet5PG9-eI/AAAAAAABHts/mj3xr3h5BTs/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t07.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-j9dZga8GI2s/VNet5PG9-eI/AAAAAAABHts/mj3xr3h5BTs/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t07.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4dIG2GPvsN8/VNet5okxOdI/AAAAAAABHt0/I-OWUFBzaUU/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t09.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-4dIG2GPvsN8/VNet5okxOdI/AAAAAAABHt0/I-OWUFBzaUU/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t09.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-r2xj5mSYqng/VNet3gVWYQI/AAAAAAABHtY/QBGyITFuaq4/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t01.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-r2xj5mSYqng/VNet3gVWYQI/AAAAAAABHtY/QBGyITFuaq4/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t01.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WqGJB7JhsnQ/VNet5cdtQZI/AAAAAAABHtw/-Li5_izEdkI/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t08.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-WqGJB7JhsnQ/VNet5cdtQZI/AAAAAAABHtw/-Li5_izEdkI/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t08.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PzaHJigi42w/VNet4trlZRI/AAAAAAABHto/jOmnLOHA6AE/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t06.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-PzaHJigi42w/VNet4trlZRI/AAAAAAABHto/jOmnLOHA6AE/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t06.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bvSXPXU7iLg/VNet4VJ5RmI/AAAAAAABHtk/WP-wJL7gDj8/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t05.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bvSXPXU7iLg/VNet4VJ5RmI/AAAAAAABHtk/WP-wJL7gDj8/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t05.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rwo1kDYFnwo/VNet4IFhs1I/AAAAAAABHtg/JVIXO2HokPQ/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t04.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rwo1kDYFnwo/VNet4IFhs1I/AAAAAAABHtg/JVIXO2HokPQ/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t04.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                 <a href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-jbqwiSXma8g/VNet3vHdxrI/AAAAAAABHuY/AHtbu4_NGFM/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t02.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-jbqwiSXma8g/VNet3vHdxrI/AAAAAAABHuY/AHtbu4_NGFM/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t02.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div style="text-align: left;">
                 <a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OdW7rZvENyo/VNet3hKJCpI/AAAAAAABHtc/KkjAN5ws81U/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t03.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; margin-bottom: 1em;">
                  <img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OdW7rZvENyo/VNet3hKJCpI/AAAAAAABHtc/KkjAN5ws81U/s1600/Barbara-Berna%CC%81t03.jpg"/>
                 </a>
                </div>
                <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/19414395/Hungarian-paper-money">
                 Hungarian Paper Moneyby Barbara Bernt
                </a>
                <br/>
                <br/>
                A series of conceptual Hungarian euro banknotes featuring European animals on one side and related plant species on the other. The original etching prints matches the proportions of the euro banknotes and even shows the skeletal structures of the animals under ultraviolet light.
                <br/>
                <blockquote class="tr_bq">
                 I designed and prepared five denominations of ten etchings, all etched in separate copper plates. This subtle and refined form of reproduction enabled me to imitate the original technique used during the production of banknotes, intaglio printing. My goal was to create a complete series with clear design, that transcends the tradition of banknote making.
                </blockquote>
               </div>

          function pageNavi(o) {
            var m = location.href,
              l = m.indexOf("/search/label/") != -1,
              a = l ? m.substr(m.indexOf("/search/label/") + 14, m.length) : "";
            a = a.indexOf("?") != -1 ? a.substr(0, a.indexOf("?")) : a;
            var g = l ? "/search/label/" + a + "?updated-max=" : "/search?updated-max=",
              k = o.feed.entry.length,
              e = Math.ceil(k / DefaultConfig.perPage);
            if (e &lt;= 1) {
              return
            }
            var n = 1,
              h = [""];
            l ? h.push("/search/label/" + a + "?max-results=" + DefaultConfig.perPage) : h.push("/?max-results=" + DefaultConfig.perPage);

              var c = (d - 1) * DefaultConfig.perPage - 1,
                b = o.feed.entry[c].published.$t,
                f = b.substring(0, 19) + b.substring(23, 29);
              f = encodeURIComponent(f);
              if (m.indexOf(f) != -1) {
                n = d
              }
              h.push(g + f + "&amp;max-results=" + DefaultConfig.perPage)
            }
            pageNavi.show(h, n, e)
          }
          pageNavi.show = function(f, e, a) {
            var d = Math.floor((DefaultConfig.numPages - 1) / 2),
              g = DefaultConfig.numPages - 1 - d,
              c = e - d;
            if (c &lt;= 0) {
              c = 1
            }
            endPage = e + g;
            if ((endPage - c) &lt; DefaultConfig.numPages) {
              endPage = c + DefaultConfig.numPages - 1
            }
            if (endPage &gt; a) {
              endPage = a;
              c = a - DefaultConfig.numPages + 1
            }
            if (c &lt;= 0) {
              c = 1
            }
            var b = '';

            if (e &gt; 1) {
              b += '&lt;a href="' + f[e - 1] + '"&gt;&lt;i class="fa fa-angle-double-left"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;'
            }
            for (i = c; i &lt;= endPage; ++i) {
              if (i == e) {
                b += '&lt;span class="current"&gt;' + i + "&lt;/span&gt;"
              } else {
                b += '&lt;a href="' + f[i] + '"&gt;' + i + "&lt;/a&gt;"
              }
            }
            if (e &lt; a) {
              b += '&lt;a href="' + f[e + 1] + '"&gt;&lt;i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;'
            }
            document.write(b)
          };
          (function() {
            var b = location.href;

              return
            }
            var d = b.indexOf("/search/label/") + 14;
            if (d != 13) {
              var c = b.indexOf("?"),
                a = (c == -1) ? b.substring(d) : b.substring(d, c);
              document.write('&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="/feeds/posts/summary/-/' + a + '?alt=json-in-script&amp;callback=pageNavi&amp;max-results=99999"&gt;&lt;\/script&gt;')

              document.write('&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="/feeds/posts/summary?alt=json-in-script&amp;callback=pageNavi&amp;max-results=99999"&gt;&lt;\/script&gt;')
            }
          })();

(function($){$.fn.ticker=function(options){var opts=$.extend({},$.fn.ticker.defaults,options);if($(this).length==0){if(window.console&amp;&amp;window.console.log){window.console.log('Element does not exist in DOM!')}else{alert('Element does not exist in DOM!')}return false}var newsID='#'+$(this).attr('id');var tagType=$(this).get(0).tagName;return this.each(function(){var uniqID=getUniqID();var settings={position:0,time:0,distance:0,newsArr:{},play:true,paused:false,contentLoaded:false,dom:{contentID:'#ticker-content-'+uniqID,titleID:'#ticker-title-'+uniqID,titleElem:'#ticker-title-'+uniqID+' SPAN',tickerID:'#ticker-'+uniqID,wrapperID:'#ticker-wrapper-'+uniqID,revealID:'#ticker-swipe-'+uniqID,revealElem:'#ticker-swipe-'+uniqID+' SPAN',controlsID:'#ticker-controls-'+uniqID,prevID:'#prev-'+uniqID,nextID:'#next-'+uniqID,playPauseID:'#play-pause-'+uniqID}};if(tagType!='UL'&amp;&amp;tagType!='OL'&amp;&amp;opts.htmlFeed===true){debugError('Cannot use &lt;'+tagType.toLowerCase()+'&gt; type of element for this plugin - must of type &lt;ul&gt; or &lt;ol&gt;');return false}opts.direction=='rtl'?opts.direction='right':opts.direction='left';initialisePage();function countSize(obj){var size=0,key;for(key in obj){if(obj.hasOwnProperty(key))size++}return size};function getUniqID(){var newDate=new Date;return newDate.getTime()}function debugError(obj){if(opts.debugMode){if(window.console&amp;&amp;window.console.log){window.console.log(obj)}else{alert(obj)}}}function initialisePage(){processContent();$(newsID).wrap('&lt;div id="'+settings.dom.wrapperID.replace('#','')+'"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');$(settings.dom.wrapperID).children().remove();$(settings.dom.wrapperID).append('&lt;div id="'+settings.dom.tickerID.replace('#','')+'" class="ticker"&gt;&lt;div id="'+settings.dom.titleID.replace('#','')+'" class="ticker-title"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;!-- --&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p id="'+settings.dom.contentID.replace('#','')+'" class="ticker-content"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="'+settings.dom.revealID.replace('#','')+'" class="ticker-swipe"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;!-- --&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');$(settings.dom.wrapperID).removeClass('no-js').addClass('ticker-wrapper has-js button=e.target.id;if(e.type=='click'){switch(button){case settings.dom.nextID.replace('#',''):settings.paused=true;$(settings.dom.playPauseID).addClass('paused');manualChangeContent('next');break;case settings.dom.playPauseID.replace('#',''):if(settings.play==true){settings.paused=true;$(settings.dom.playPauseID).addClass('paused');pauseTicker()}else{settings.paused=false;$(settings.dom.playPauseID).removeClass('paused');restartTicker()}break}}else if(e.type=='mouseover'&amp;&amp;$('#'+button).hasClass('controls')){$('#'+button).addClass('over')}else if(e.type=='mousedown'&amp;&amp;$('#'+button).hasClass('controls')){$('#'+button).addClass('down')}else if(e.type=='mouseup'&amp;&amp;$('#'+button).hasClass('controls')){$('#'+button).removeClass('down')}else processContent(){if(settings.contentLoaded==false){if(opts.ajaxFeed){if(opts.feedType=='xml'){$.ajax({url:opts.feedUrl,cache:false,dataType:opts.feedType,async:true,success:function(data){count=0;for(var false}settings.contentLoaded=true;setupContentAndTriggerDisplay()}})}else{debugError('Code Me!')}}else if(opts.htmlFeed){if($(newsID+' LI').length&gt;0){$(newsID+' false}}else{debugError('The ticker is set to not use any types of content! setupContentAndTriggerDisplay(){settings.contentLoaded=true;$(settings.dom.titleElem).html(settings.newsArr['item-'+settings.position].type);$(settings.dom.contentID).html(settings.newsArr['item-'+settings.position].content);if(settings.position==(countSize(settings.newsArr)-1)){settings.position=0}else{settings.position++}distance=$(settings.dom.contentID).width();time=distance/opts.speed;revealContent()}function pauseTicker(){settings.play=false;$(settings.dom.tickerID+','+settings.dom.revealID+','+settings.dom.titleID+','+settings.dom.titleElem+','+settings.dom.revealElem+','+settings.dom.contentID).stop(true,true);$(settings.dom.revealID+','+settings.dom.revealElem).hide();$(settings.dom.wrapperID).find(settings.dom.titleID+','+settings.dom.titleElem).show().end().find(settings.dom.contentID).show()}function
